# Documentation Standards

## README Requirements
- Purpose in one sentence
- Quick start (3-5 commands max)
- Prerequisites listed upfront
- Examples before theory

## Code Documentation
- Why, not what
- Document surprises, not obvious code
- Public APIs: always document
- Complex logic: inline explanation

## Format
- Markdown for all docs
- Relative links between docs
- Code examples in fenced blocks with language tags
